Fn+Alt		MACRO_STATE_NONE	Help message
		

Fn+Alt+Spc	MACRO_STATE_REC_INIT	Record Macro / Enter macro number
		MACRO_STATE_REC_LOCK	Locked(Enter) / Unlocked(Backspace)
		MACRO_STATE_REC_TYPE	Type Macro

Fn+Alt+[0-9]	MACRO_STATE_INIT	Play Macro

Fn+Alt+Del	Delete macros
		Enter macro number
		Enter

Fn+Alt+Enter	Unlock Macros
		<Password><Enter> > unlock
		Bs
			Clear password and locked macros?
			Enter
			New password
			Enter			

Fn+Alt+Bspc	Lock Macros	
		
